  "texts": [
    "The Selective Kernel (SK) Attention Module brings in an approach to adjust the importance of the feature maps, enabling the model to pay attention to significant regions in the input data.",
    "This selective attention mechanism empowers YOLOv8-CAB to prioritize features while downplaying ones, enhancing object detection accuracy.In the context of small object detection, this innovation becomes particularly advantageous.",
    "By leveraging the SK Attention Module, YOLOv8-CAB becomes more adept at capturing these nuances, thus enhancing YOLOv8-CAB's ability to identify small objects accurately.",
    "On the other hand, attention mechanisms in deep learning models directly affect the decision-making process.",
    "Attention allows the model to focus on specific input parts more relevant to the task."
  ],
